 dropdown"><a title='Information for HttF attendees' class='nav-link dropdown-toggle' href="#" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">Attendees</a><ul class="dropdown-menu glass" aria-labelledby="navbar"><li class="index-1 first"><a title='Venue' class='nav-link ' href="/2019/venue">Venue</a></li><li class="index-2"><a title='Hotel' class='nav-link ' href="/2019/hotel">Hotel</a></li><li class="index-3"><a title='Registration' class='nav-link ' href="/2019/registration">Registration</a></li><li class="index-4"><a title='SIGCHI Student Rate' class='nav-link ' href="/2019/sigchi-student-subsidy">SIGCHI Student Rate</a></li><li class="index-5"><a title='Code of Conduct' class='nav-link ' href="/2019/conduct">Code of Conduct</a></li><li class="index-6 last"><a title='Visas and Brexit' class='nav-link ' href="/2019/visas-and-brexit">Visas and Brexit</a></li></ul></li><li class="index-4 nav-item dropdown"><a title='Programme information for the symposium' class='nav-link dropdown-toggle' href="#" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">Programme</a><ul class="dropdown-menu glass" aria-labelledby="navbar"><li class="index-1 first"><a title='Programme' class='nav-link ' href="/2019/programme">Programme</a></li><li class="index-2"><a title='Keynote speakers' class='nav-link ' href="/2019/keynotes">Keynote speakers</a></li><li class="index-3"><a title='Symposium themes' class='nav-link ' href="/2019/themes">Symposium themes</a></li><li class="index-4 last"><a title='Feedback' class='nav-link ' href="/2019/feedback">Feedback</a></li></ul></li><li class="index-5 nav-item dropdown"><a title='Details about the organising committee and programme committee' class='nav-link dropdown-toggle' href="#" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">Organisers</a><ul class="dropdown-menu glass" aria-labelledby="navbar"><li class="index-1 first active"><a title='Organising Committee' class='nav-link ' href="/2019/organising-committee">Organising Committee</a></li><li class="index-2 last"><a title='Programme Committee' class='nav-link ' href="/2019/programme-committee">Programme Committee</a></li></ul></li><li class="index-6 last"><a title='Details about sponsoring the symposium' class='nav-link ' href="/2019/sponsorship">Sponsors</a></li></ul><!--<form method="get" action="/2019/search" class="form-block nav-search"><input type="search" class="form-control nav-search-input pull-right" name="search" placeholder="Searchâ€¦" value=""></form>--></nav></div></div></header><div class="row"><div class="main-container container-fluid"><div class="main row p-md-4 pt-sm-2 p-sm-1 pt-2 p-0 shadow"><div class="breadcrumb-container col-12"><nav aria-label="breadcrumb" class="shadow rounded"><ol class="breadcrumb"><li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/2019/">Halfway to the Future</a></li><li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="#">Organisers</a></li><li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">Organising Committee</li></ol></nav></div><div class="col-12"><h1>Organising Committee</h1></div><div class="col-xl-9 col-lg-8 col-md-7 col-12"><article><div data-bolt-field="teaser"><div><p>The <strong>Halfway to the Future symposium</strong> has been put together by the following members of the <a href="http://www.mrl.nott.ac.uk/" title="The Mixed Reality Laboratory at the University of Nottingham">Mixed Reality Lab</a> at the University of Nottingham. If you are contacting a member of the committee regarding the symposium, please use the symposium email addresses included below as this helps to filter email in relation to the event in our inboxes!</p></div></div><div class="card record-card shadow rounded" data-bolt-field="body"><div class="card-body"><h5 class="card-title">General Chairs</h5><p><a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/research/groups/mixedrealitylab/people/joel.fischer" title="Joel's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Joel E. Fischer</a>, <a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/clas/departments/culturalmediaandvisualstudies/people/sarah.martindale" title="Sarah's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Sarah Martindale</a>, <a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/research/groups/mixedrealitylab/people/martin.porcheron" title="Martin's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Martin Porcheron</a>, <a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/research/groups/mixedrealitylab/people/stuart.reeves" title="Stuart's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Stuart Reeves</a>, and <a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/research/groups/mixedrealitylab/people/jocelyn.spence" title="Jocelyn's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Jocelyn Spence</a></p><p><em>Email: <a href="mailto:general-chairs@halfwaytothefuture.org" title="Email all five General Chairs">general-chairs@halfwaytothefuture.org</a></em></p><p><strong>Administration Manager</strong><br><a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/computerscience/people/lindsay.norman" title="Lindsay's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Lindsay Norman</a></p></div></div><div data-bolt-field="body"class="d-lg-flex "><div class="col-lg-6 col-12 pr-1 p-0 "><p><strong>Programme Chairs</strong><br><a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/research/groups/mixedrealitylab/people/joel.fischer" title="Joel's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Joel E. Fischer</a><br><a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/research/groups/mixedrealitylab/people/stuart.reeves" title="Stuart's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Stuart Reeves</a><br><a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/research/groups/mixedrealitylab/people/jocelyn.spence" title="Jocelyn's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Jocelyn Spence</a></p><p><em>Email: <a href="mailto:programme@halfwaytothefuture.org" title="Email both Programme Chairs">programme@halfwaytothefuture.org</a></em></p><p><strong>Communications &amp; Marketing Chair</strong><br><a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/research/groups/mixedrealitylab/people/martin.porcheron" title="Martin's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Martin Porcheron</a></p><p><em>Email: <a href="mailto:comms@halfwaytothefuture.org" title="Email the Communications Chair">comms@halfwaytothefuture.org</a></em></p><p><strong>Sponsorship Chair</strong><br><a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/research/groups/mixedrealitylab/people/stuart.reeves" title="Stuart's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Stuart Reeves</a></p><p><em>Email: <a href="mailto:sponsorship@halfwaytothefuture.org" title="Email the Sponsorship Chair">sponsorship@halfwaytothefuture.org</a></em></p><p><strong>Local Arrangements Chair</strong><br><a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/clas/departments/culturalmediaandvisualstudies/people/sarah.martindale" title="Sarah's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Sarah Martindale</a></p><p><em>Email: <a href="mailto:local@halfwaytothefuture.org" title="Email the Local Arragenments Chair">local@halfwaytothefuture.org</a></em></p><p><strong>Equality, Diversity, and Inclusion Chair</strong><br><a href="https://www.horizon.ac.uk/researchers/" title="Pepita is a member of the Horizon Digital Economy Research Institute at the University of Nottingham">Pepita Barnard Stringer</a></p><p><em>Email: <a href="mailto:edi@halfwaytothefuture.org" title="Email the Equality, Diversity, and Inclusion Chair">edi@halfwaytothefuture.org</a></em></p></div><div class="col-lg-6 col-12 pl-lg-1 p-0 "><p><strong>Keynote Chair</strong><br><a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/research/groups/mixedrealitylab/people/stuart.reeves" title="Stuart's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Stuart Reeves</a></p><p><em>Email: <a href="mailto:keynote@halfwaytothefuture.org" title="Email the Keynote CHair">keynote@halfwaytothefuture.org</a></em></p><p><strong>Demos Chair</strong><br><a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/research/groups/mixedrealitylab/people/edgar.bodiaj" title="Edgar's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Edgar Bodiaj</a><br><a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/research/groups/mixedrealitylab/people/paul.tennent" title="Paul's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Paul Tennent</a><br> Joe Marshall (Paternity Leave)</p><p><em>Email: <a href="mailto:technical@halfwaytothefuture.org" title="Email the Demos Chair">demos@halfwaytothefuture.org</a></em></p><p><strong>Technical Chair</strong><br><a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/research/groups/mixedrealitylab/people/adrian.hazzard" title="Adrian's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Adrian Hazzard</a></p><p><em>Email: <a href="mailto:technical@halfwaytothefuture.org" title="Email the Techincal Chair">technical@halfwaytothefuture.org</a></em></p><p><strong>Treasurer &amp; Registration Chair</strong><br><a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/research/groups/mixedrealitylab/people/martin.porcheron" title="Martin's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Martin Porcheron</a></p><p><em>Email: <a href="mailto:treasurer@halfwaytothefuture.org" title="Email the Treasurer and Registration Chair">treasurer@halfwaytothefuture.org</a></em></p><p><strong>Communications &amp; Marketing Assistant</strong><br><a href="https://highlights.cdt.horizon.ac.uk/students/psxavsp" title="Velvet is a student in the Horizon Centre for Doctoral Training at the University of Nottingham">Velvet Spors</a></p><p><strong>Administrative Assistants</strong><br><a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/computerscience/people/lindsay.norman" title="Lindsay's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Lindsay Norman</a><br><a href="https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/computerscience/people/felicia.black" title="Felicia's profile on the University of Nottingham website">Felicia Black</a></p></div></div></article></div><aside class="col-xl-3 col-lg-4 col-md-5 col-12"><div class="card shadow rounded" class="p-2"><div class="card-body"><h5 class="card-ti